-> The CSS used in this website is from the Tails wind
    To use it you have to link it first in the head tag
        <link href="https://unpkg.com/tailwindcss@^2/dist/tailwind.min.css" rel="stylesheet">    

-> The images that changes everytime you reload the website is added using the unsplash

-> The main Header, Main body and Footer is taken from the Tail winds block, as we linked the Tails wind CSS we have used their blocks to create the pages

-> The database used here is Firebase a google cloud console database which is 24/7 online and no need to worry about it getting shutdown.

-> To link the database to the page you need to link using the script source
    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/firebase/7.14.1-0/firebase.js"></script>
paste it in the page you want to connect the database

-> The user info. is trasfered from website to the database using the javascript, This javascript can be used only if you made an app in the project of Firebase.

-> The code for the app of Firebase project is in the different files with .js at the end and those files and linked to the page using the...
    <script src="APP_NAME.js"></script>

-> The alert messages after the clicking submit in the feedback or the contact us form is taken from the sweet alerts website, first need to link their css 
    <script src="https://unpkg.com/sweetalert/dist/sweetalert.min.js"></script>
and then you can add the alert messages where ever you want.

-> The website is hosted using the Github pages, The domain is linked to the IP of the DNS servers of the github page using the BigRock domain website.

-> The Domain = codebydurvesh.com